The paper proposes an algorithm to accelerate DNN training and demonstrates its effectiveness on computer vision datasets. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
